"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"In Lebanon, Israeli strikes have killed at least 31 people, according to the health ministry. Israel says it was responding to attacks from Hezbollah using drones and rockets.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israeli Strikes in Lebanon\",            \"translated_version\": \"En L\u00edbano, ataques de Israel han matado al menos a 31 personas, dice el ministerio de salud. Israel dice que respond\u00eda a ataques de Hezbollah con drones y cohetes.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataques de Israel en L\u00edbano\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Iran's attacks on Gulf Arab states suggest that the country is targeting not only the US military but also civilian infrastructure. Several deaths have been reported across the Middle East as Tehran retaliates for large strikes by the US and Israel.\",            \"english_title\": \"Iran's Attacks on Gulf States\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los ataques de Ir\u00e1n a estados \u00e1rabes del Golfo sugieren que el pa\u00eds est\u00e1 atacando no solo al ej\u00e9rcito de EE.UU. sino tambi\u00e9n a infraestructura civil. Se han reportado varias muertes en el Medio Oriente mientras Teher\u00e1n responde a grandes ataques de EE.UU. e Israel.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataques de Ir\u00e1n a Estados del Golfo\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Experts have warned that a long conflict could make global energy prices go even higher.\",            \"english_title\": \"Energy Prices Warning\",            \"translated_version\": \"Expertos han advertido que un conflicto largo podr\u00eda hacer que los precios de energ\u00eda global suban m\u00e1s.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Advertencia de Precios de Energ\u00eda\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"India and Canada are working to finish a trade deal by the end of the year as their leaders try to improve relations in Delhi.\",            \"english_title\": \"India-Canada Trade Deal\",            \"translated_version\": \"India y Canad\u00e1 est\u00e1n trabajando para terminar un acuerdo comercial para fin de a\u00f1o mientras sus l\u00edderes intentan mejorar relaciones en Delhi.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Acuerdo Comercial India-Canad\u00e1\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Growing insecurity in the Sahel made 2025 one of the worst years for the kidnapping of foreigners in Africa.\",            \"english_title\": \"Insecurity in the Sahel\",            \"translated_version\": \"La creciente inseguridad en el Sahel hizo que 2025 fuera uno de los peores a\u00f1os para el secuestro de extranjeros en \u00c1frica.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Inseguridad en el Sahel\"        }    ]}"